.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH vibe 1  "vibe " 
.SH NAME
vibe \- Vibe Runtime packaging and development tool
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBvibe\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIsubcommands\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Vibe Runtime packaging and development tool
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
vibe\-init(1)
Initialize a new Vibe application project
.TP
vibe\-validate(1)
Validate a vibe.yaml manifest
.TP
vibe\-package(1)
Package a Vibe application into a .vibeapp archive
.TP
vibe\-sign(1)
Sign a .vibeapp package
.TP
vibe\-verify(1)
Verify a signed .vibeapp package
.TP
vibe\-keygen(1)
Generate an Ed25519 signing keypair
.TP
vibe\-import\-compose(1)
Import from Docker Compose (coming soon)
.TP
vibe\-inspect(1)
Inspect a .vibeapp package
.TP
vibe\-revert(1)
Strip saved user state (_vibe_state/*) from a .vibeapp, restoring original signed content
.TP
vibe\-install\-hooks(1)
Install AI coding assistant skills for Vibe development (Claude, Codex, Cursor, Copilot)
.TP
vibe\-help(1)
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
